{"tid":754188,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[福音] 美國政府讓步 3D打印手槍時代來臨","createTime":"2018-07-24T08:05:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-24T08:49:09.000Z","uid":17103,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"fba422d4fd91c3f0856c9f3dcec26811dab60dcc","tid":754188,"uid":17103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T08:05:09.000Z","msg":"<strong>美國政府讓步 3D打印手槍時代來臨</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180724/large/1532380846_a4c7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180724%2Flarge%2F1532380846_a4c7.png&h=1dfc111e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180724/58478418\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180724%2F58478418&d=%2FrI7eD%2F6V29ZkNZAC5nNgGMi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=f89afa6b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180724%2F58478418&h=b9ef9f0d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180724/58478418</a><br />\n<br />\n美國政府跟一名3D打印手槍設計師在法庭達成和解，8月1日起人們將可以購買手槍藍圖，在家使用3D打印機，和ABS塑膠樹脂自行製作塑膠槍械。<br />\n<br />\n美國國務院上月跟設計師威爾遜（Cody Wilson）在法庭達成和解，為3D打印槍械開綠燈。威爾遜的公司Defense Distributed揚言：「可下載槍械的年代正式開始。」<br />\n<br />\n槍械管制支持者對此感到擔憂，認為和解「非常危險」，「已定罪的重犯和家暴者可從網上下載圖表，打印非法而無法追蹤的槍械」，呼籲國務院繼續阻止這類「致命信息（deadly information）」出版。<br />\n<br />\n威爾遜設計的軟件，為單發3D打印手槍「The Liberator」的藍圖。國務院認為，提供藍圖等如違反武器出口法規，要求威爾遜停止這項工作。<br />\n<br />\n威爾遜以設計受到憲法《第一修正案》保護辯護，更成立非牟利機構Defense Distributed，以資助官司費用。<br />\n<br />\n該機構售賣手槍零件「80%完成度下機匣」（80% lower）以及銑床（milling machine）。前者被美國政府視為槍械完成度只有80%的金屬，加上銑床後，買家配合電腦和軟件，就能生產出一把沒有序列號、不受傳統槍械管制法限制的「鬼槍」（ghost gun）。<br />\n<br />\n將來，用家只要下載3D打印藍圖，便可以在家中使用3D打印機，自行製作「The Liberator」或其他款式如AR-15來福槍，不用購買「80%完成度下機匣」。這類槍械不需要金屬撞針來運作，<span style=\"color: red;\">但藍圖中包括一片額外金屬，以來確保手槍遵守《不可探測槍支法案》(Undetectable Firearms Act)，通過金屬探測器時可以被搜出。</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c8d9b607d91f723fd6c9f0817231e33dfb6f438","tid":754188,"uid":106468,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T08:12:22.000Z","msg":"睇左3D打手槍"},{"pid":"42450e88ec8f5b80ec103dc16c28730b3e06a9e7","tid":754188,"uid":28181,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T08:14:20.000Z","msg":"但藍圖中包括一片額外金屬，以來確保手槍遵守《不可探測槍支法案》(Undetectable Firearms Act)，通過金屬探測器時可以被搜出。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/fac